public int minAddition(String s, String t) {
    int sLen = s.length();
    int tLen = t.length();
    int i = 0, j = 0;
    while (i < sLen && j < tLen) {
        if (s.charAt(i) == t.charAt(j)) {
            j++;
        }
        i++;
    }
    return tLen - j;
}
```

